Import profile

Usage: wheelctl profile import [OPTIONS] <PATH>

Arguments:
  <PATH>  Profile file path

Options:
      --json             Output in JSON format for machine parsing
  -t, --target <TARGET>  Target directory
  -v, --verbose...       Verbose logging
      --verify           Verify signature
  -h, --help             Print help
